[[File:Putin presidential international trips.png|thumb|500px|World map highlighting countries visited by Vladimir Putin during his presidency, as of {{monthyear}}. {{legend|#a1a7ef|One visit}} {{legend|#737ce8|Two visits}} {{legend|#4f5ae3|Three visits}} {{legend|#2533dd|Four visits}} {{legend|#1a25ac|Five visits}} {{legend|#111976|Six visits}} {{legend|#0a1053|Seven or more visits}} {{legend|#da0000|Russia including the [[Political status of Crimea|disputed]] [[Crimea|Crimean Peninsula]]}} ]] {{Putin sidebar}}
This is a list of '''presidential trips made by [[Vladimir Putin]]'''. During [[Presidency of Vladimir Putin|his presidency]], which began with his inauguration on May 7, 2000, he has traveled to 50 different countries internationally as of March 2008, in addition to many more trips made domestically within Russia.
