os]]. Attended the [[APEC Chile 2004|APEC]] summit. |- |{{flag|Brazil}} |[[Brasília]] |November 22 |Official visit. Met with President [[Luiz Inácio Lula da Silva]]. |- |{{flag|Portugal}} |[[Lisbon]] |November 23 |Met with President [[Jorge Sampaio]] and Prime Minister [[Pedro Santana Lopes]]. |- |{{flag|Netherlands}} |[[Hague]] |November 25–26 |Attended the Russia-EU summit. |- |{{flag|India}} |[[New Delhi]], [[Bangalore]] |December 3–5 |Official visit. Met with Prime Minister [[Manmohan Singh]] and President [[Abdul Kalam]]. |- |{{flag|Turkey}} |[[Ankara]] |December 5–6 |Official visit. Met with Prime Minister [[Recep Tayyip Erdoğan]] and President [[Ahmet Necdet Sezer]]. |- |{{flag|Germany}} |[[Schleswig-Holstein]] |December 20–21 |Met with Chancellor [[Gerhard Schröder]]. |}
